# Tech Stack Overview

## Package manager
 - Bun

## Frontend:
 - Vue 3: Modern, reactive framework for building the user interface.
 - Tailwind CSS: Utility-first CSS framework for responsive and customizable UI design.
 - TypeScript: Adds static typing to JavaScript, improving code quality and maintainability.

## Backend & Core:
 - Rust: High-performance systems programming language for core logic and backend operations.
 - Tauri 2: Framework for building lightweight, secure, and cross-platform desktop applications. Combines Rust for backend and web technologies for frontend.